@demonflyingfox just made “Breaking Bad by Balenciaga” and you’d think a fashion house actually commissioned it.

Remember when “X by Balenciaga” was just a meme template with cursed AI faces and warped hands? That was 2023. This version has real fabric texture, real camera movement, and character styling that looks like it came off an actual runway shoot in the desert.

